{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS LINKS AT THE END OF THIS PAGE -->
__FORCETOC__

== Usage ==

'''{{Tl|ODNBsub}}''' can be used without parameter. If used in conjunction with a {{Tl|cite web}} (or similar) or {{Tl|citation}} template, it should be placed between the closing brackets of the template and the </ref> tag, in the same way as with {{Tl|subscription required}}.

* <code><nowiki>{{ODNBsub}}</nowiki></code> generates the note to be used in a sentence &rarr; {{ODNBsub}}
* <code><nowiki>{{ODNBsub|sentence=yes}}</nowiki></code> generates the note being a proper sentence &rarr; {{ODNBsub|sentence=yes}}

== See also ==
* {{Tl|ODNBweb}}, a template which includes {{Tl|ODNBsub}}
* {{Tl|Subscription or libraries}}
* {{tl|Subscription or membership required}}, which has the same text, but doesn't link anywhere

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
